px; font-family: normal;">out</text><text class="draggable" name="text" x="84" y="21" r="0" rtemp="0" transform="rotate(0 84  21)" style="fill: rgb(255, 123, 0); font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-size: 13px; font-family: normal;">in</text><g transform="translate(388,15)" x="388" y="15" title="codeHTML" width="375" height="357" class="codeHTML" name="codeHTML" rot="0"><foreignObject x="0" y="0" width="222" height="200" style="height: 595px; width: 625px;"><div name="htmlCode" style="zoom: 60%; height: 595px; width: 625px;" code="<div class=&quot;ch&quot;>
    
    <h1>RC Low-Pass Filter - SPICE AC Analysis</h1>

    <div class=&quot;ch-card&quot;>
        <h2>Circuit Components</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Resistor (R1):</strong> 1 k&amp;Omega;</li>
            <li><strong>Capacitor (C1):</strong> 1 &amp;micro;F</li>
            <li><strong>Input (V1):</strong> AC Voltage Source (1V amplitude)</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <h2>Cutoff Frequency</h2>
    <div class=&quot;ch-formula&quot;>
        fc = 1 / (2&amp;pi;RC) = 1 / (2&amp;pi; &amp;times; 1000 &amp;times; 1&amp;times;10&amp;minus;6) &amp;approx; <strong>159 Hz</strong>
    </div>

    <h2>Simulation Results</h2>
    <div class=&quot;ch-grid&quot;>

        <div class=&quot;ch-col blue&quot;>
            <h3>Magnitude Response (Black Line)</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Pass Band:</strong> 0 dB gain for f &amp;lt; 159 Hz</li>
                <li><strong>Cutoff Point:</strong> -3 dB drop at 159 Hz</li>
                <li><strong>Stop Band:</strong> -20 dB/decade roll-off</li>
                <li>At 10 kHz, attenuation is approx -35 dB</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class=&quot;ch-col red&quot;>
            <h3>Phase Response (Red Line)</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Low Freq:</strong> 0&amp;deg; phase shift</li>
                <li><strong>At Cutoff (fc):</strong> -45&amp;deg; (-0.785 rad)</li>
                <li><strong>High Freq:</strong> Approaches -90&amp;deg; (-&amp;pi;/2 rad)</li>
                <li>Capacitor introduces a lagging phase shift</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

